data.description: Welcome to your dream hill country retreat! This stunning 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home is situated on a 0.275-acre lot, offering hill country views that will take your breath away. As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by a covered 2-car parking area and a convenient circular driveway, providing ample space for parking and easy access to the front entrance. Step inside and be impressed by the unique open floor plan that sets this home apart. The interior boasts a split primary bedroom and office on one side of the home, providing a private and secluded retreat. The primary bedroom features ample space, large windows that showcase natural sunlight, and an ensuite bathroom with modern fixtures, and a double vanity. On the other side of the home, you'll find the remaining 3 bedrooms, perfect for family members or guests. Each bedroom is well-appointed with ample closet space. The 2 additional bathrooms are conveniently located, making them easily accessible from each bedroom. Step outside to the backyard oasis and you'll find an inviting covered porch bordered with a privacy fence, providing a serene and tranquil setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing and enjoying the surrounding natural beauty. In 2020, all windows and doors have been upgraded. Come see what Holiday Villages of Medina Lake has to offer!
